Cell["\<\
To see the effect of the additional phase factors, add randomly chosen phase \
factors to the initial reduced Gottesman matrix:\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1490427478,ExpressionUUID->"d98efe3b-1e0a-44a3-982e-8342959a2a03"],

